statement.title: Problem Description
statement.content: Your task is to calculate the sum of some integers.

statement.title: Input
statement.content: Input contains multiple test cases, and one case one line. Each case starts with an integer N, and then N integers follow in the same line.

statement.title: Output
statement.content: For each test case you should output the sum of N integers in one line, and with one line of output for each line in input.
